replyContent:
Ability to put custom logo on a receipt will be added in a future version.
Currently there are no plans of adding the save as PDF feature to the app. Receipts can only be saved as PNG images at this time.

content: To make this app really useful, I would recommend the following: 1. Have a settings menu that would allow us to add the name of the receipt signer once as the default.  2. As above let the "for" category be set up for several user defined options like "rent, dues, donations,  etc." 3. Add the abilty to email the receipt when completed to an entered email address or one from my phone contact list. 4. Automaticly email copy of receipt to my own email address.  The above adds would rock this app.
replyContent:
(#3) Version 3 added ability to email receipt from within the app. User can enter a new email address or add from contacts list.
(#1) & (#4) will be added in next update.
(#2) may be added in a future update.
